 (x_i, y_i) \rightarrow \text{coordinates of microphone #i}\\ C = 340.29 m/s 
 (x, y) \rightarrow \text{coordinates of source} \\ t_i \rightarrow \text{time of arrival of sound to microphone #i} \\ D_i = C \times t_i \rightarrow \text{distance between source and microphone #i} 
 Di = ti * C = \sqrt{ (x - xi)^2 + (y - yi)^2 }\\ t1 = \frac{1}{C} * \sqrt{ (x - x1)^2 + (y - y1)^2 }\\ t2 = \frac{1}{C} * \sqrt{ (x - x2)^2 + (y - y2)^2 }\\ t3 = \frac{1}{C} * \sqrt{ (x - x3)^2 + (y - y3)^2 } 
 t1 - t2 = \frac{1}{c} (\sqrt{ (x - x1)^2 + (y - y1)^2 } - \sqrt{ (x - x2)^2 + (y - y2)^2 })\\ t1 - t3 = \frac{1}{c} (\sqrt{ (x - x1)^2 + (y - y1)^2 } - \sqrt{ (x - x3)^2 + (y - y3)^2 }) 
